    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors correctly scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates hemolysis index predictions within 15% of bench measurements across the CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in support of pre-market submission. No unresolved weakeners identified.",
